type: web_research
title: "US Options Trading Automation System - Tools, MCP, APIs, Libraries Research"
key_insights[10]: Alpaca is the only broker with an official MCP server supporting live options trading,ThetaGang is the most mature open-source options bot (Wheel strategy) for Interactive Brokers,"Alpha Vantage, Financial Datasets, EODHD, and Bright Data all offer MCP servers for financial data",IEX Cloud has shut down - no longer available,ib_async is the successor to ib_insync for Interactive Brokers Python integration,TradingAgents is a multi-agent LLM framework with 7 specialized roles for trading,QuantConnect LEAN supports options backtesting with free historical data,Tastytrade has both official and unofficial Python SDKs for options automation,Schwab API replaced TD Ameritrade - schwab-py is the migration path,Jake Nesler's experiment showed Claude Code can autonomously trade options with Alpaca
findings[10]: "MCP Servers: Alpaca (live trading), Alpha Vantage, Financial Datasets, EODHD, Massive/Polygon, Bright Data, MCP-Trader/Maverick","Brokers with Python APIs: Interactive Brokers (ib_async), Alpaca (alpaca-py), Tastytrade (tastytrade SDK), Tradier, Schwab (schwab-py), Webull (official SDK)","Options Backtesting: QuantConnect LEAN, Backtrader, OptionLab, Optopsy, Backtesting.py","Greeks Libraries: py_vollib, QuantLib-Python, Mibian","Data Providers: Polygon.io/Massive (OPRA feed), Alpha Vantage, EODHD, yfinance (free)","Apify Actors: Reddit Sentiment Analyzer, Twitter Cashtag Scraper, Yahoo Finance Scraper, Stock Sentiment Data Scraper","Claude Skills: claude-trading-skills (tradermonty), claude-equity-research, Investment Analysis skill on mcpmarket","OSS Bots: ThetaGang, LoopTrader, PyOptionTrader, MMR, python-trading-robot","AI Trading Frameworks: AI-Trader (HKUDS), TradingAgents (TauricResearch), Aurora",SkillsMP has 87K+ Claude Code skills including finance/trading category
refs[8]: "https://github.com/brndnmtthws/thetagang - ThetaGang IBKR bot","https://github.com/alpacahq/alpaca-mcp-server - Alpaca MCP Server","https://github.com/TauricResearch/TradingAgents - Multi-agent trading","https://github.com/HKUDS/AI-Trader - AI trading benchmark","https://github.com/9600dev/mmr - MMR trading platform","https://github.com/financial-datasets/mcp-server - Financial Datasets MCP","https://github.com/ib-api-reloaded/ib_async - IB async Python","https://github.com/tastyware/tastytrade - Tastytrade Python SDK"
recommendations[7]: Use Alpaca MCP Server as primary broker integration for Claude Code,Use ThetaGang as reference architecture for Wheel strategy automation,"Deploy multiple MCP servers: Alpaca (trading) + Alpha Vantage/EODHD (data) + Bright Data (scraping)",Use TradingAgents framework architecture for multi-agent analysis,Combine yfinance (free data) with Polygon.io (premium real-time),Use Apify for Reddit/Twitter sentiment analysis pipeline,Consider QuantConnect LEAN for options backtesting with free data
